boreali in gold explor pact with faraway & lt ; boreali explor ltd > said it enter into an agreement with & lt ; faraway gold mine ltd > of vancouv , british columbia , under which faraway will acquir an interest in boreali 's whale cove gold properti in the keewatin district of the northwest territori . faraway will spend 1.5 mln dlr on explor over three year and will hold 50 pct of the properti until all expens are paid out , when the interest will drop to 40 pct . also , boreali and faraway will issu treasuri share to each other and faraway will buy 575,000 boreali share from boreali presid lorn spenc .